Business Card App 

  

App Description 

Allows people to make their own business cards and make them fully customizable. 

  

General App Attributes 

Category: Design App 

Mobile: Easy to make Business cards and add variety to them as well. 

Story: To introduce yourself to someone and leave them a way to contact you later. Make a business card for any encounter 

Market: All people usually need a way to let people they meet contact each other the first time they meet. 

Habit: Any time you meet a potential business acquaintance you want to leave a good impression on them.  

Scope: Version 1 allows to make simple templates and save to be used later. version 2 lets people purchase pre-made templates. 

  

